# Azenquoria Development Guidelines

## State Management
- Use `setState` for state management (no Provider/Riverpod initially)
- Keep state management simple and localized to widgets when possible

## Data Storage
- Use `shared_preferences` for local data storage
- No external databases or cloud storage required

## Code Organization
- Follow the folder structure defined in project-structure.mdc
- Keep widget files focused on a single responsibility
- Extract reusable widgets to the widgets directory

## Package Restrictions
- Do NOT use:
  - `freezed` package or part syntax
  - External fonts
  - `cached_network_image`
  - Asset images (no assets/images/ folder)

## Feature Implementation Notes
- No user account functionality required
- All text should be in Chinese
- QR code generation should work offline
- Breathing exercises should have smooth animations
 